end="02:59.455" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L35"><span begin="02:57.821" end="02:58.205">夏</span><span begin="02:58.205" end="02:58.389">が</span><span begin="02:58.389" end="02:58.839">遠</span><span begin="02:58.839" end="02:59.015">く</span><span begin="02:59.015" end="03:00.767">て。</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">夏天也渐渐远去了</span></p><p begin="03:00.767" end="03:03.303" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L36"><span begin="03:00.767" end="03:00.983">こ</span><span begin="03:00.983" end="03:01.191">れ</span><span begin="03:01.191" end="03:01.359">で</span><span begin="03:01.359" end="03:01.455">も</span><span begin="03:01.455" end="03:01.767">本</span><span begin="03:01.767" end="03:01.975">当</span><span begin="03:01.975" end="03:02.079">に</span><span begin="03:02.079" end="03:02.210">い</span><span begin="03:02.210" end="03:02.341">い</span><span begin="03:02.341" end="03:02.472">ん</span><span begin="03:02.472" end="03:02.647">で</span><span begin="03:02.647" end="03:02.887">す</span><span begin="03:02.887" end="03:03.535">か。</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这样真的好吗</span></p><p begin="03:03.535" end="03:06.176" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L37"><span begin="03:03.535" end="03:03.736">こ</span><span begin="03:03.736" end="03:03.920">の</span><span begin="03:03.920" end="03:04.095">ま</span><span begin="03:04.095" end="03:04.295">ま</span><span begin="03:04.295" end="03:04.495">生</span><span begin="03:04.495" end="03:04.680">き</span><span begin="03:04.680" end="03:04.864">て</span><span begin="03:04.864" end="03:05.056">も</span><span begin="03:05.056" end="03:05.165">い</span><span begin="03:05.165" end="03:05.274">い</span><span begin="03:05.275" end="03:05.384">ん</span><span begin="03:05.384" end="03:05.665">で</span><span begin="03:05.665" end="03:05.824">す</span><span begin="03:05.824" end="03:06.353">か。</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我能接受 就这么活下去吗</span></p><p begin="03:06.353" end="03:11.010" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L38"><span begin="03:06.353" end="03:06.533">そ</span><span begin="03:06.533" end="03:06.713">ん</span><span begin="03:06.713" end="03:06.914">な</span><span begin="03:06.914" end="03:07.122">の</span><span begin="03:07.122" end="03:07.521">君</span><span begin="03:07.521" end="03:07.713">に</span><span begin="03:07.713" end="03:07.890">し</span><span begin="03:07.890" end="03:08.048">か</span><span begin="03:08.048" end="03:08.231">わ</span><span begin="03:08.231" end="03:08.415">か</span><span begin="03:08.415" end="03:08.576">ら</span><span begin="03:08.576" end="03:08.736">な</span><span begin="03:08.736" end="03:08.936">い</span><span begin="03:08.936" end="03:09.104">よ</span><span begin="03:09.104" end="03:09.268">な</span><span begin="03:09.268" end="03:09.408">ん</span><span begin="03:09.408" end="03:09.609">て</span><span begin="03:09.609" end="03:09.809">言</span><span begin="03:09.809" end="03:10.000">わ</span><span begin="03:10.000" end="03:10.169">れ</span><span begin="03:10.169" end="03:10.408">ま</span><span begin="03:10.408" end="03:10.561">す</span><span begin="03:10.561" end="03:11.060">か。</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你会告诉我 答案只有你能明白吗</span></p><p begin="03:11.010" end="03:14.552" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L39"><span begin="03:11.010" end="03:11.304">た</span><span begin="03:11.304" end="03:11.737">だ</span><span begin="03:12.009" end="03:12.392">夏</span><span begin="03:12.392" end="03:12.577">の</span><span begin="03:12.577" end="03:12.937">匂</span><span begin="03:12.937" end="03:13.129">い</span><span begin="03:13.129" end="03:13.297">に</span><span begin="03:13.297" end="03:13.480">目</span><span begin="03:13.480" end="03:13.664">を</span><span begin="03:13.664" end="03:14.000">瞑</span><span begin="03:14.000" end="03:14.192">り</span><span begin="03:14.192" end="03:14.528">た</span><span begin="03:14.528" end="03:14.807">い。</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我只想闭上眼 闻一闻夏日的气息</span></p><p begin="03:14.807" end="03:17.356" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L40"><span begin="03:14.807" end="03:15.016">い</span><span begin="03:15.016" end="03:15.199">つ</span><span begin="03:15.199" end="03:15.368">ま</span><span begin="03:15.368" end="03:15.568">で</span><span begin="03:15.568" end="03:15.746">も</span><span begin="03:15.746" end="03:16.104">風</span><span begin="03:16.104" end="03:16.288">に</span><span begin="03:16.288" end="03:16.464">吹</span><span begin="03:16.464" end="03:16.648">か</span><span begin="03:16.648" end="03:16.840">れ</span><span begin="03:16.840" end="03:17.199">た</span><span begin="03:17.199" end="03:17.636">い。</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">任凭清风拂过</span></p><p begin="03:17.636" end="03:21.300" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L41"><span begin="03:17.636" end="03:18.020">青</span><span begin="03:18.020" end="03:18.388">空</span><span begin="03:18.388" end="03:18.572">だ</span><span begin="03:18.572" end="03:18.748">け</span><span begin="03:18.748" end="03:18.835">が</span><span begin="03:18.835" end="03:18.994">見</span><span begin="03:18.994" end="03:19.170">た</span><span begin="03:19.170" end="03:19.411">い</span><span begin="03:19.411" end="03:19.587">の</span><span begin="03:19.587" end="03:19.771">は</span><span begin="03:19.771" end="03:20.139">我</span><span begin="03:20.139" end="03:20.499">儘</span><span begin="03:20.499" end="03:20.659">で</span><span begin="03:20.659" end="03:20.890">す</span><span begin="03:20.890" end="03:21.476">か。」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只想看着蓝天 难道也算是一种任性吗”</span></p><p begin="03:23.348" end="03:26.998" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L42"><span begin="03:23.348" end="03:23.523">あ</span><span begin="03:23.523" end="03:23.708">な</span><span begin="03:23.708" end="03:23.899">た</span><span begin="03:23.899" end="03:24.083">だ</span><span begin="03:24.083" end="03:24.283">け</span><span begin="03:24.283" end="03:24.484">を</span><span begin="03:24.484" end="03:24.668">知</span><span begin="03:24.668" end="03:24.835">り</span><span begin="03:24.835" end="03:25.083">た</span><span begin="03:25.083" end="03:25.135">い</span><span begin="03:25.135" end="03:25.295">の</span><span begin="03:25.295" end="03:25.470">は</span><span begin="03:25.470" end="03:25.838">我</span><span begin="03:25.838" end="03:26.181">儘</span><span begin="03:26.181" end="03:26.350">で</span><span begin="03:26.350" end="03:26.558">す</span><span begin="03:26.558" end="03:26.998">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只想了解关于你的一切 也算是种任性吗</span></p></div></body></tt>